Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.75,0:01:16.74,r,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}出会いに色はなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.00,0:01:19.92,r,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}モノクロ吹き抜ける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.07,0:01:25.48,r,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}涼しい指 手招くままに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.65,0:01:28.82,r,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}溶けた後の厄介な
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.08,0:01:32.14,r,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}氷みたいな私を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.85,0:01:35.27,r,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}優しく救って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.45,0:01:38.79,r,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}上唇で遊ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.10,0:01:43.05,r,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}それでも一つの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.17,0:01:46.18,r,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}愛の形を探す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.31,0:01:50.09,r,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}遠くよりも今を結んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.25,0:01:52.91,r,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}かれた瞳を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:55.87,r,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}できればこのまま
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:01:58.93,r,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}包まれて終わりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.06,0:02:02.91,r,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}その願いは夜は虚しく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:05.93,r,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}朝を連れてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:09.35,r,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}優しくて熱くて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.46,0:02:12.20,r,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}不幸なキスで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:15.79,r,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}彩ってよ最後の夜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.96,0:02:19.70,r,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}月が照らしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.75,0:01:16.74,z,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}与你的邂逅并无他色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.00,0:01:19.92,z,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}微风吹拂过黑白两色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.07,0:01:25.48,z,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}冰冷的手指一如既往地在召唤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.65,0:01:28.82,z,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}仿佛就像融化后的冰霜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.08,0:01:32.14,z,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}一样陷入绝境的我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.85,0:01:35.27,z,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}温柔地被你拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.45,0:01:38.79,z,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}玩弄于上唇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.10,0:01:43.05,z,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}即使如此也在寻找着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.17,0:01:46.18,z,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}一种爱的形态
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.31,0:01:50.09,z,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}比起遥远的未来不如约定现在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.25,0:01:52.91,z,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}将这双干枯的瞳眸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:55.87,z,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}尽可能地就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:01:58.93,z,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}被拥抱着迎来终结
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.06,0:02:02.91,z,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}这个愿望把黑夜抽离
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:05.93,z,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}将清晨送达于此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:09.35,z,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}用这温柔又火热
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.46,0:02:12.20,z,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}代表不幸的吻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:15.79,z,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}将最后之夜渲染上彩色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.96,0:02:19.70,z,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}月光照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,度假村度假村
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.32,0:00:05.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.51,0:00:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,度假村度假村
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.29,0:00:09.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.70,0:00:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厲害啊梅琳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.23,0:00:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好感動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.30,0:00:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 居然能帶我們一起去女王大人的修養地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.85,0:00:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們家的少爺 還是有不錯的地方的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.50,0:00:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.98,0:00:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是幸福的人們啊 看來被感謝了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.42,0:00:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫柔的少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.36,0:00:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為如果只留下他們 把別墅弄壞的話我也很困擾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.82,0:00:34.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.94,0:00:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來這裏就是村子的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.43,0:00:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我忘記提醒你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.68,0:00:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏是那個度假村的建設預定場地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.17,0:00:56.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爺……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.04,0:02:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個執事，遊蕩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.92,0:02:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是去旅行嗎 在這個時節
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞巴斯蒂安 你知道“虐熊”這種休閑活動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.31,0:02:48.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs24}（charlotte russe:俄式奶油夾心布丁）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.91,0:02:48.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說好像是很娛樂有著令人著迷的反響
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.76,0:02:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不巧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脖子上套著繩索的熊 被鬥犬所包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.04,0:02:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撕咬它 直到死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.98,0:03:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可真是 很像人類所為啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.46,0:03:06.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然在1835年頒布的防止虐殺動物法中被禁止了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這部法令上有漏洞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.94,0:03:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於虐殺方是狗的並不適用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.88,0:03:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢 會發生什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.22,0:03:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗就會虐狗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:18.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 “虐狗”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.39,0:03:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有進行著那種活動的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍恩茲華斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本是因飼養獵犬而出名的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.28,0:03:27.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那個村子裏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.76,0:03:42.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的心在滴血
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:46.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個村子正以保養地的名義被保護著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.92,0:03:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是這次旅行的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是狗的村子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.65,0:03:52.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麽了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 確保用地這種工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於少爺來說真是細微的瑣事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的 在那個名為霍恩茲華斯的村子裏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:09.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有著我法多姆海恩不得不出面的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.06,0:04:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 發現第一個村民
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:30.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,田中先生 停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來幫你 老婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不行啊 菲尼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.60,0:04:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不小心點的話 裏面的嬰兒會…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.99,0:04:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.33,0:04:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.44,0:04:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嬰兒沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個孩子啊 被那東西吃掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.24,0:05:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被吃了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:03.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs24}（杵逆的黑狗是壞狗）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:12.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個村子裏好像有很多行蹤不明或是被殘暴殺害的村民
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.07,0:05:16.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這十年裏人口減少了三分之一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其原因的糾察和排除
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.69,0:05:20.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是交給我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:28.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs24}（過來吧 我會把你連骨骸都吃得一幹二凈）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.87,0:05:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像變得像樣起來了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下(sit)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.61,0:05:57.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躺下(lie down)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 孩子 不錯 孩子(ok boy good boy)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.43,0:06:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想被這樣疼愛一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用糖果和鞭子扭曲他的意識 強迫他順從
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:11.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是感人的場面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:13.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是狗就是狗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對人搖尾乞憐 十分樂意地被套上頸圈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是無法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.72,0:06:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想說什麽就直說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.91,0:06:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麽恭敬不如從命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.13,0:06:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我十分熱愛貓 但是卻不太喜歡狗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.40,0:06:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說白了就是討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:58.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是法多姆海恩伯爵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.79,0:06:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.88,0:07:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎您來到巴裏姆卡斯宅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.09,0:07:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人正在恭候您的大駕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.39,0:07:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個漂亮的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊請
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.22,0:07:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個吉娃娃是怎麽回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說了讓你去迎接女王的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉娃娃…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.65,0:07:40.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你連那點事沒辦法完成嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞巴斯蒂安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.22,0:07:48.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹什麽 你這個下人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.54,0:07:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要頂撞我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放開我混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:53.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我命令他的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.37,0:07:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.59,0:07:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來信已經送到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:08:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是夏爾.法多姆海恩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.51,0:08:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是說像你這樣的小不點狗就是女王陛下的使者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對小型犬有什麽不滿嗎 亨利卿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別發呆 菲尼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快搬 快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏由我來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒得談
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論你開出什麽條件 我都無法同意收購
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我聽聽理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.32,0:08:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為有鬼作祟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.43,0:08:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼作祟？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.01,0:08:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從古至今與狗一同生活到現在的這個村子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:50.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若有人想對它出手的話就會出現鬼作祟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.64,0:08:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐懼的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.15,0:08:56.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是女王陛下 那也不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:09:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個村子裏與我巴裏姆卡斯家族作對的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.41,0:09:03.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都會有巨大的災難降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.46,0:09:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔？ 真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.45,0:09:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.18,0:09:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就讓我看看所謂的災難吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.00,0:09:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清清楚楚地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女仆只有你一個人嗎 這個別墅裏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:24.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厲害啊 我很尊敬你 安吉拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒那種事 我還不夠成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.35,0:09:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有我們能幫忙的事 盡管開口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都是下人 就好好相處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧 菲尼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.41,0:09:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 當然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.58,0:09:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真溫柔啊 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 主人在叫我了 我先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:03.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿 她說我溫柔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,餵 菲尼 你在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.79,0:10:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安吉拉 安吉拉喲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女王想要把我的村子……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:28.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定能理解我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.33,0:10:30.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會守護住這個村子的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.76,0:10:37.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安吉拉 我的天使喲 我的天使喲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.52,0:10:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到了 我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.10,0:10:47.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉深夜打擾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.73,0:10:54.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爺馬上就要休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.02,0:10:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有個請求
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.61,0:11:00.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你們迅速離開這個村子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.01,0:11:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能待在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.63,0:11:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.04,0:11:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.33,0:11:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.43,0:11:14.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔犬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.46,0:11:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔犬？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.46,0:11:21.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞巴斯蒂安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.06,0:11:26.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爺 看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.39,0:11:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是魔犬大人 魔犬大人出現了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.99,0:11:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰 誰是惡犬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:46.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爺 安吉拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.99,0:11:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這到底是發生了什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔犬出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.75,0:11:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔犬？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為村子帶來災害的人 杵逆主人的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.53,0:11:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都會被魔犬所懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.91,0:12:02.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是這個村子的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:04.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安吉拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請轉告巴裏姆卡斯先生 說魔犬大人出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰受到了處罰？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.64,0:12:20.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.00,0:12:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.06,0:12:26.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要碰他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.15,0:12:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惡犬是詹姆斯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 這個人違反了五條規定 養了第六條狗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣啊 那就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:41.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麽叫沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個村子裏有我制定的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,違法規定的人就會被守護我們巴裏姆卡斯家族的魔犬所懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs24}（白狗是好狗）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:13:02.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs24}（杵逆的黑狗是壞狗）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.87,0:13:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為是你們這群外人被處罰了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.61,0:13:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撿回一條命了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.09,0:13:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.41,0:13:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺是最差的旅行吶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.03,0:13:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麽了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.07,0:13:51.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,途中明明那樣高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.45,0:13:52.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘記了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.94,0:13:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是來度假的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麽 什麽啊 這不是很舒適嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.73,0:14:10.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水也並不涼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.50,0:14:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅琳裏也快來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.47,0:14:16.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我果然很害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.68,0:14:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得的好機會哦 好了 快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.15,0:14:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果 果然很丟人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.28,0:14:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很漂亮哦 梅琳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.19,0:14:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摘下眼睛肯定會更好的不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.08,0:14:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.37,0:14:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是從少爺那裏得到的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.97,0:14:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爺不去遊泳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.54,0:14:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是那樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爺…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.06,0:14:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個季節還可以遊泳說明這裏還是有作為保養地的價值呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你當真打算把這裏變成保養地嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.27,0:15:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔犬要怎麽辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.27,0:15:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也發覺了不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只魔犬的真身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:13.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借我一下耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安傑拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,yes my lord 那麽就立刻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.54,0:15:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意外的有幹勁呢 你不是討厭狗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.98,0:15:30.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很討厭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.75,0:15:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想盡快收拾幹凈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.84,0:15:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在成為最糟的發展之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.41,0:15:44.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安傑拉也請
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.49,0:15:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就連我也一起招待真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然 很好吃的塞巴斯蒂安的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.60,0:15:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓到了 抓到壞狗了 塞姆斯的狗 懲罰 懲罰要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.88,0:16:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只狗好像在咬著什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.47,0:16:08.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吐出來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.07,0:16:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松嘴 混蛋 這條壞狗 松嘴 松嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是頑固又壞的狗呢 開始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.04,0:16:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很可憐嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.73,0:16:56.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.74,0:17:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲尼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:07.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妨礙了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,0:17:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把神聖的懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,壞家夥又
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.36,0:17:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是壞狗 壞狗 給予壞狗懲罰 給予壞狗懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.27,0:17:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 活該 小不點狗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.66,0:17:28.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人務必請求您饒恕這些人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.87,0:17:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 這個小不點狗好歹也是女王陛下的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據談話結果也可以饒過你們哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:43.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從這個村莊撤手 並且向女王陛下進言永遠不會再碰觸這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.57,0:17:48.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了保護這種惡心王國 不惜做到那種程度嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.76,0:17:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛獸就是為了形容你們這種人才存在的詞語
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.55,0:17:57.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麽就讓你知道違抗我的壞狗會怎麽樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:17:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.28,0:18:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.89,0:18:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.35,0:18:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,my lord
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.48,0:18:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:17.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要礙事嘛 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.56,0:18:18.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在做什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.17,0:18:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我連著他一起咬死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:25.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多麽煩人細碎的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.80,0:18:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才討厭狗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.72,0:18:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發 發生了什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.54,0:18:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬧劇就到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.89,0:18:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴裏姆卡斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:41.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽著 村民們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並不存在魔犬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.43,0:18:46.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在的只有被權利的猛獸所咬的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.51,0:18:48.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個可悲的老人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:50.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你有什麽根據
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.82,0:18:51.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.83,0:18:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在宅邸的地下發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.23,0:18:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已確認牙印與吉姆斯的傷口吻合
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.46,0:19:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請看這便是魔犬的真身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:10.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔犬的影子只是投影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.55,0:19:13.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過是騙小孩的把戲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.31,0:19:15.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閃光的身影是磷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.51,0:19:19.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把磷撒在普通狗的身上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.75,0:19:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔犬不過是由一個人所演出來的幻像
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後這個人就是你 亨利巴裏姆卡斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.30,0:19:34.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那麽 你有什麽證據證明是我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我吧 你的使命已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上等布料 為什麽這只狗在最後都沒有放開這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.12,0:19:55.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理由就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:19:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.25,0:20:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 它為了保護吉姆斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.08,0:20:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而咬你的腳並撕下來的褲子一角
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.09,0:20:13.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺掉吉姆斯的是你嗎 沒有什麽魔犬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.12,0:20:14.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你騙了我們的啊\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.66,0:20:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,認命吧 你已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.50,0:20:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕不饒恕 絕不饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.54,0:20:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原諒我\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.01,0:20:35.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厲害啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.03,0:20:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到最後都要保護主人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.42,0:20:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很努力了 很努力了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.48,0:21:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才討厭狗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.17,0:21:16.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就搞定了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.79,0:21:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨停了就離開村子
